title: DiCUNO B22 to E27 Socket Converter, Socket Adapter, Bayonet to Screw Edison, BC to ES Lamp Base Adapter for LED Bulbs and Incandescent Bulbs and CFL Bulbs-2 Packs
features: Basic Information: DiCUNO B22 to E27 Converter/ Bayonet to Screw is easy to install, whose max wattage is 200W, and voltage is 0-250V with 165℃ high-temperature resistance.
Reliable Guarantee: Our BC to ES Socket Adapter is Upgrade→There is no iron ring inside the lamp holder, which makes your installation process safer. ▲Please CUT OFF the power before installation.
Easy Installation: No need for extra tools to install, simply screw the socket adapt into B22/Bayonet socket, then screw in E27/Screw type bulb.

Wide Application: This Bayonet to Screw Edison Lamp Base Adapter is ideal for LED, halogen, filament, or CFL light bulb, which allows you to choose more LED lights to adapt to your fixture or base, rather than replace your fixtures with a new one.
Warranty: 3-month refund and 1-year warranty. Immediate customer service! If you have any problem, please feel free to contact us. We are always here for you.
